<lb n="0202b19" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="038" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="38" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>經律異相卷第三十八<note place="inline">優婆夷<note n="0202014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">部＋（第二十八）【明】</note><note n="0202014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">部【大】，部第二十八【明】</note><app n="0202014"><lem wit="【大】">部</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">部第二十八</rdg></app></note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
